                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-95-off458 t17900526-95-cd459"></join> last, one feather bed, value 20 s. one bolster, value 3 s. two woollen blankets, value 2 s. one pair of sheets, value 2 s. one iron stove, value 2 s. 6 d. one brass fender, value 2 s. one shovel, value 6 d. one iron poker, value 6 d. one pair of tongs, value 6 d. a looking glass, value 6 d. a copper saucepan, value 18 d. one set of harrateen bed furniture, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900526-95-victim872" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Beecham
                        <interp inst="t17900526-95-victim872" type="surname" value="Beecham"></interp>
